General.Name: Dustin Group AB
General.Description: Dustin Group AB (publ) provides online IT products and services in Nordic and Benelux regions. It operates through three segments: Small and Medium-Sized Businesses, Large Corporate and Public Sector, and Business to Consumer. The company offers hardware, software, and related services and solutions. It also acts as a strategic IT partner for small and medium-sized businesses, large sized businesses, and public sector and consumers. The company was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in Nacka Strand, Sweden.
